The paper deals with path planning for a UAV in a cellular network, which involves communication and control aspects. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also proposes a graph theory-based solution for the path planning problem, which falls under the scope of cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also utilizes channel gain maps and SINR maps, which are related to information theory and signal processing, respectively, and hence, cs.IT (Information Theory) is another likely category. The paper also involves optimization and decision-making, which are related to cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), respectively.
